                            Islamic times. The Gospel of the Twelve Apostles and related texts’, in
                                <title rend="italic">La Syrie, de Byzance à l’Islam</title>, <abbr>ed.</abbr> P.
                            Canivet and J.-P. Rey-Coquais (1992), 67–74.</bibl>
                        <bibl>J. R. Harris, <title rend="italic">The Gospel of the <choice>
                                    <sic>XII</sic>
